                 PORT     NAME     PORT      BEHAVIOR
*tcp*            *0*      *x*      *x*        *Dedicated client, fails
                                             if immediately connecting
                                             to a               server
                                             on the other side fails*
udp              0        x        x         Dedicated client
raw              0        x        0         Dedicated client, works
                                             only as `root'
*tcp, udp*       *x*      *x*      *x*        *Client, switches to
